data.description: RARE OPORTUNITY, Newly renovated home features 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths. The home was remodeled in July of 2023. Ample living room with high ceilings, a fire place and large windows that provide plenty of natural light. The wrap around kitchen includes marble countertops, high efficiency stainless steal appliances with gas range and beautiful upgraded fixtures and hardware.  The primary suite comes with high ceilings large closet and a luxurious primary bathroom with a soaking tub, separate shower and dual vanity. Walking distance to the community pool and play ground.
